                                       │
                                       ├─► README · architecture &amp; as-built  ── committed to <b>main</b> (diffable in git)
                                       └─► marketing <b>site</b> (en · de · fr · es) ── parity-checked
                                       │
            in-app <b>help drawer</b>  ── summary · getting started · key actions · fields &amp; filters · tips</pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

